  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [X] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nforge 0.2.0 (7b45265 2023-11-21T00:18:30.267248000Z)\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\nforge fmt\n\n### Operating System\n\nmacOS (Apple Silicon)\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nWhen saving a file in vscode with auto save enabled, forge does not auto format the file anymore, even though nothing was changed in fmt settings in foundry.toml\r\n\r\nThis only started to happen in the most recent foundry version.\r\n\r\nUsing vscode Version: 1.84.2 (latest version)",
